<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy - Medi Point</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        body {
            background: #f8fafc;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            color: #334155;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .privacy-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            width: 100%;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1), 0 2px 4px -2px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #0f172a;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .date {
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #1e293b;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            color: #475569;
        }
        ul {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        li {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #475569;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .back-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 32px;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background: #2563eb;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 15px;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }
        .back-btn:hover {
            background: #1d4ed8;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="privacy-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p class="date">Last updated: July 4, 2026</p>
        </div>
        
        <p>Welcome to Medi Point. We are committed to protecting your personal information and your right to privacy.</p>
        
        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We collect personal information that you voluntarily provide to us when you register on our platform, schedule appointments, or contact us. This includes:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Names, contact details (emails, phone numbers).</li>
            <li>Schedule preferences and doctor availability.</li>
            <li>Google Calendar authentication tokens when linking your account.</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information we collect to provide and maintain the core features of Medi Point, including booking appointments, sending email notifications, and syncing event details with Google Calendar.</p>
        
        <h2>3. Google Calendar Integration</h2>
        <p>Medi Point requests permission to manage your Google Calendar events. This connection is used strictly to create, modify, and delete appointments booked directly through this platform. We never access your personal calendars unrelated to Medi Point, and your authentication tokens are stored securely.</p>
        
        <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
        <p>We implement a variety of security measures to maintain the safety of your personal information. Your tokens and session cookies are stored securely on our database and client devices.</p>
        
        <h2>5. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions or comments about this policy, you may contact us at support@medi-point.com.</p>
        
        <a href="/" class="back-btn">Back to Portal</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
